# Phase gate and evidence

Every completed slice must report:

- decision
- worktree, branch and HEAD
- scope and exclusions
- relevant prototype references
- exact files read and changed
- current vs target distinction
- tests and build results
- runtime/browser evidence where relevant
- migration status
- privacy/security boundary
- known limitations and watch items
- exact staged files
- commit/push status only if authorised
- evidence file path
- next gate

Update the live tracker, master build plan, phase plan and `report.md` only after the change and evidence are accepted.
